Caledonia Plasma Theme Changelog
--------------------------------

*_v1.2 Sep 28 2012

-KDE 4.9.x Compatible
-Added an icon for Bangarang
-Better audio icons
-Added SLC icons
-Better opaque support (without KWin effects)
-New icon for Apper/KPackageKit
-Better network icons (and new wired connection icons)
-Revised preferences icons (and new icon for KRandTray)
-New Korgac icon
-Revised KMess icon
-Added KNotes icon
-Removed Skype and VLC icons (not systray support in both)
-Improved calendar
-Added plot background changes
-Panel improvements
-Added phone icon (for test)
-Added KAlarm icon
-Revised branding
-New KTeatTime icon
-Removed battery-oxygen widget
-Improved Kopete icon
-Added Konqueror icon
-Added dialog icons
-Added KTimer icon
-Added Record It Now icon
-Revised colors
-Updated documentation
-New containment controls
-Improved/revised notifications
-Added drop-indicators for Icon Tasks
-Revised extender-background
-Added a CSS stylesheet for news plasmoid
-Revised view item

