(...LEGACY VERSIONS...)

Caledonia Plasma Theme changes the license (move to Creative Commons) in Oct 14 2011 (version 0.9.8) because of many new components.
Only versions prior to 0.9.8 keeps the GPL license. See the metadata to know the Caledonia version.